data.description: This Asperline log home offers a log exterior and on the interior, all wood doors and trim and is situated just perfectly on the wooded 1.44-acre lot.  The lower level offers a door that enters the partially finished basement from the driveway and a garage with access to the partially finished basement. As you go to the main level you will be greeted by a beautiful rich log home interior of wood planking on the walls, exposed wood beams, tongue, and grove wood ceilings and lots of natural light.  The window shades are solar shades to keep the heat in during winter and out during the summer.  Looking up at the vaulted ceiling you will be amazed at the richness of the wood and the natural light provided by the skylights.  Aside from the breathtaking ambiance created by the log home interior the first floor offers you two bedrooms, full bath, open concept living room, kitchen, and dining area. and a foyer that leads you to the large screen porch and a six-person hot tub.  If that is not enough let’s go to the second floor using the open staircase to the loft and sanctuary of the primary bedroom with a large walk-in closet and en suite bathroom that offers a jetted tub and separate shower.  There is more this home offers much but I will leave that for when you take your private tour to discover the hidden and not so hidden treasures that make this home and property one of a kind. Furnishings can be negotiated to remain separate from sale of the real estate.  Considering a VRBO?
